<br>
For now, once you reach Qeynos, you can hunt in West Karana and Blackburrow, the entrance to which is in Qeynos Hills. <br>
<br>
Once you achieve level twelve, I strongly suggest Erudin's Crossing. The zone is beautiful, rarely crowded and is perfect for a 12-16 Magician. Pull wisps down to the beach, right down by the water, and fight them there. Use your F9 key to see the big picture, and move your battles if another wisp or KOS mob approaches.<br>
<br>
 You'll get a lot of BO lightstones, but if you put in some time you'll eventually come out with a nice haul of Greater Lightstones and Lightstones, which sell for about four and one platinum, respectively.<br>
<br>
Forte<br>
62 Magician<br>
