on the journeys to cross the great continent of antonica you need to seriously consider to download all the maps of all the zones that you will cross, trust me, if you dont you gonna get lost and die.  go to the www.eqatlas.com and get them.  if you dont you may be sorry.  but let me say this, buy the PoP just for the sake of the free portals that you will get, this will save you so much time and deths its not even going to be funny.  <br>
<br>
also before you travel anywhere make sure to get SoW which will make you run fast.  do NOT attempt any long crossings across zones where there is mobs (monsters) that will kill you without SoW.  SoW is spirit of the wolf but just ask for SoW and they will know what you mean.<br>
<br>
try to stay away from the kithlicor forest if you can.  that zone will mess you up good, no joking.  if you do happent oto go into this zone, dont follow the paths.  both of the zone connection can be reached by following the right wall all the way to rivedale and highpass hold.  if you go into highpass hold go INVIS as soon as you zone in cuz there will be orcs that will kill you near.  and you know there is always that 1 cheeky monkey that will be bringing 8 orcs to the zone. lol watch it<br>
<br>
if you have any other questions post them to here and i will give you an answer asap<br>
